<div class="explanation">
  <p class="paragraph">A community board dedicated to enhancing students of Trilogies' ability to connect with peers, allowing for an improved learning experience through peer experience sharing. You can click on recent issues below, or make your own issue by creating an account or logging in.</p>
{{#if logged_in}}
  <div class="create-btn-box">
    <a href="/create"><button class="create-btn">Create a Post</button></a>
  </div>
{{/if}}
